00:00:10.920 --> 00:00:15.150
we're faced with a stark choice. Either
you can be materialistic and that means

00:00:15.150 --> 00:00:19.710
obsessed with money and possessions
shallow and selfish, or you can reject

00:00:19.710 --> 00:00:25.260
materialism be good and focus on more
important matters of the Spirit. But in

00:00:25.260 --> 00:00:29.699
